I have one more
slide I want to do.

00:35:15.975 --> 00:35:17.350
What some of you
may want to know

00:35:17.350 --> 00:35:18.620
is where does that water go.

00:35:18.620 --> 00:35:20.680
Similar to what I said
before, is agriculture

00:35:20.680 --> 00:35:22.990
is the biggest user of it,
household use, industry,

00:35:22.990 --> 00:35:23.860
and so forth.

00:35:23.860 --> 00:35:27.100
But I will stop here
