00:35:58.690 --> 00:36:05.190
SETH SIEGEL: Yeah, so the
interest group-- the answer

00:36:05.190 --> 00:36:08.300
is that there are
strong interest groups.

00:36:08.300 --> 00:36:14.080
And so what ends up happening is
