00:36:14.080 --> 00:36:19.830
and has been going for quite
a while, between kind of three

00:36:19.830 --> 00:36:22.470
or four interest groups--
the environmental groups,

00:36:22.470 --> 00:36:27.940
speaking on behalf of the rivers
and the fish, the farmers,

00:36:27.940 --> 00:36:29.740
and the city-dwellers.

00:36:29.740 --> 00:36:34.970
And there's also
a legal structure

00:36:34.970 --> 00:36:36.660
